    <a title="Patricia Horton-gerschler" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/27972828-patricia-horton-gerschler"><img alt="Patricia Horton-gerschler" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1390487401p2/27972828.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
