<span id="freeTextContainer16055401204605531517">The Subtle Beauty is a twisted tale of a princess who doesn&apos;t realize she&apos;s burdened with the beastly curse of vanity. Her sisters are also obliviously cursed with the seven deadly sins. Lucky for them they have a loving father and king who knows them better than they themselves and matches them to husbands who are their balance. How often do we not realize our burdens and stubbornly resist yielding to the will of the Father? The Subtle Beauty reminds us that what we want isn&apos;t always what we ne</span>
  <span id="freeText16055401204605531517" style="display:none">The Subtle Beauty is a twisted tale of a princess who doesn't realize she's burdened with the beastly curse of vanity. Her sisters are also obliviously cursed with the seven deadly sins. Lucky for them they have a loving father and king who knows them better than they themselves and matches them to husbands who are their balance. How often do we not realize our burdens and stubbornly resist yielding to the will of the Father? The Subtle Beauty reminds us that what we want isn't always what we need and love often comes from the most unexpected places.</span>
